title: 2Pac - Legit Rarities, B-Sides, and Guest Appearances (1993-1998
description:
This is a collection of non-album tracks by the late, great 2pac Shakur. The time period spans 1993-1998 because I included the "new" releases that were on the Greatest Hits album. The sound quality of all of these tracks are all very good and they are from various other rapper's albums, soundtracks, etc. I spend what seemed like ages researching and going through old albums to find these of which I feel are some of his better rarities to make yet another double disc in his honor. However, unlike "Until the End of Time" & "Better Dayz", most of these tracks were released while he was still with us in the physical form. I arranged these tracks for hopes of straight through listenability. I made this mix a few years ago and have altered it very little. Now its time to share it with the world.


So, download it, give it a listen, and please seed my hard work. All 2pac fans deserve to hear this great collection! For most people, there may be at least one of these songs that you have never heard before from way back in the day! Its worth checking out right?

-WiShBone
